column5: hello  I am planning to go out tue and wed for some ice fishing.  I have been at  Rice and Scugog last week and did quite well.  If you dont have gear thats Ok I have tons of extras,   I have POP UPS, underwater cameras, X67c ice machine tons of PAN FISH and walleye tackle/  Let me know via  PM'S or give my home number a call  (289) 240-6313  Dave
might want to check regs on walleye on rice.
Never said I was walleye fishing on Rice  all I said is that I have tons of "Walleye" and Pan-fish gear.  DIV 17  Walleye's on Scugog only  Dave
Hey I'm in the same situation up in sudbury.  Too bad we didn't live closer.......
I went to Scugog on Saturday, and got skunked! I went to Birch Island and was wondering where you caught your fish on Scugog.  I'm thinking of trying again this weekend.
Sounds like a good offer, too bad I'm not closer......Good Luck!
